🌙LunaMix

Beauty like a moonlight

LunaMix is merge model that has beautiful and relistic features.

HuggingFace

This model is merged using Chattiori's Model Merger

🧪Merge Recipe

  • Sum Twice, ChillyMix-V2 + midmix-v2.0 + BlessingMix-V1, rand_alpha(0.2, 0.6, 6319827 ) rand_beta(0.2, 0.65, 2321835) >> TEMP-1A

  • Sum Twice, XtReMiXUltiMateMerge-v1.5 + XXMix_9realistic-v4.0 + majicMIXrealistic-v6, rand_alpha(0.1, 0.7, 362481 ) rand_beta(0.4, 0.75, 8163924) >> TEMP-1B

  • Sum Twice, Milky-Chicken-v1.1 + MixAnimeRealistic-V1.9F + AddictiveFuture_Realistic_SemiAsian-V1, rand_alpha(0.15, 0.65, 3361475 ) rand_beta(0.2, 0.65, 9143023) >> TEMP-1C

  • Sum Twice, TEMP-1A + kisaragi_mix-v2.2 + ShampooMix-v4, rand_alpha(0.1, 0.65, 351723 ) rand_beta(0.25, 0.75, 7153851) >> TEMP-2A

  • Sum Twice, TEMP-1B + ThisIsReal-V1 + X-FlareMix-Real, rand_alpha(0.15, 0.7, 3197455 ) rand_beta(0.2, 0.6, 672481) >> TEMP-2B

  • Sum Twice, TEMP-1C + VivCharMix-v5_NewEra + KawaiiRealisticAsianMix-v0.3, rand_alpha(0.1, 0.55, 4615283 ) rand_beta(0.2, 0.6, 7153994) >> TEMP-2C

  • Sum Twice, TEMP-2A + TEMP-2B + TEMP-2C, rand_alpha(0.1, 0.55, 7315854 ) rand_beta(0.1, 0.55, 6142873) >> LunaMix

⚙Recommended Settings:

  • Sampler: “DPM++ SDE Karras” recommended.

  • Steps: 20~

  • Clipskip: 1 or 2

  • CFG Scale: 7 or higher recommended.

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

🖌Recommended Prompt:

Prompt : (8k, best quality, masterpiece:1.2), (realistic, photo-realistic:1.37), ultra-detailed,

Negative : (deformed,distorted,disfigured:1.3),poorly drawn,bad anatomy,wrong anatomy,extra limb,missing limb,noating limbs,(mutated hands and finger:1.4),disconnected limbs,mutabon,mutated,ugly,disgusting,blurry,amputation

🔍Recommended Upscaler:

  • Upscaler: Latent(nearest-exact)

  • Denoising strength: 0.5 ~ 0.6

  • Hires steps: 20 ~

  • Upscale by: 1.5 ~

✨Recommended Embeds:

  • bad hands

  • Easy Negative

  • Easy Negative V2

  • Deep Negative

  • Pure Eros Face

  • veryBadImageNegative
